{"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Type Method","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setUserId:completion:","kind":"identifier"}],"symbolKind":"method","role":"symbol","title":"setUserId:completion:","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setUserId:completion:"}],"modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)setUserId:completion:"},"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setuserid:completion:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets a custom user identifier with completion confirmation."}],"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ ("},{"text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setUserId:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"NSString","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"userId"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"completion:"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"kind":"text","text":" (^"},{"text":")(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSError","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSError"},{"kind":"text","text":" * "},{"text":"error","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":")) "},{"text":"completion","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"userId","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The custom user identifier (e.g., database ID, UUID, username)."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Block called when the operation completes."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Receives nil on success, or an NSError on failure.","type":"text"}]}],"name":"completion"}]},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Same as "},{"code":"setUserId:","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" but provides callback when the server operation completes.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Use this when you need to ensure the user ID is set before performing","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"dependent operations like merging user data or tracking critical events.","type":"text"}]},{"text":"Example","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Example"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Handle login with guaranteed user ID synchronization:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","code":["class LoginCoordinator {","","    func performLogin(credentials: Credentials,","                      completion: @escaping (Result<User, Error>) -> Void) {","","        APIClient.shared.login(credentials) { result in","            switch result {","            case .success(let user):","                \/\/ Set user ID with confirmation before proceeding","                Pushwoosh.configure.setUserId(user.id) { error in","                    if let error = error {","                        Logger.warning(\"User ID sync failed: \\(error.localizedDescription)\")","                        \/\/ Continue anyway - local state is still valid","                    }","","                    \/\/ Now safe to track login event with correct user attribution","                    Pushwoosh.configure.setTags([","                        \"logged_in\": true,","                        \"last_login\": ISO8601DateFormatter().string(from: Date()),","                        \"login_method\": credentials.method.rawValue","                    ])","","                    \/\/ Set email if available","                    if let email = user.email {","                        Pushwoosh.configure.setEmail(email)","                    }","","                    completion(.success(user))","                }","","            case .failure(let error):","                completion(.failure(error))","            }","        }","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift"}],"kind":"content"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setUserId:completion:"},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/setUserId:completion:":{"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"setUserId:completion:"}],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setuserid:completion:","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"Sets a custom user identifier with completion confirmation.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setUserId:completion:","title":"setUserId:completion:","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setUserId:completion:"}]},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK."}],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","role":"collection","title":"PushwooshCore"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"PWConfiguration","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[],"title":"PWConfiguration","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration"}}}